title: Our Top 10 Favorite Albums Of All Time | Ear Biscuits Ep.298
description:
From albums that have influenced their own music to albums that evoke memories of long distance relationships and California drives, R&L count down their top 10 favorite albums of all time in this episode of Ear Biscuits!
Also be sure to check out our playlist with a song from each of these albums on the Rhett and Link Spotify account!
